Over there!

525
00:41:36,887 --> 00:41:39,117
Let go of me! Over there!

526
00:41:39,256 --> 00:41:40,848
Calm down!

527
00:41:40,991 --> 00:41:42,515
Let go of me!

528
00:41:42,660 --> 00:41:48,292
He's over there! l'm fine!

529
00:42:19,229 --> 00:42:20,992
l think you might be in danger.

530
00:42:23,400 --> 00:42:25,800
lf you need help, call me.

531
00:42:28,639 --> 00:42:31,130
Kelvin, US secret service.

532
00:42:42,119 --> 00:42:44,314
l'm sorry there were so many casualties.

533
00:42:47,658 --> 00:42:49,922
l think somebody
wanted to silence Greg Li.

534
00:42:51,362 --> 00:42:52,522
We'll look into it.

535
00:42:54,164 --> 00:42:56,462
l'll fly to Singapore tomorrow
to explain things.

536
00:42:57,334 --> 00:42:59,063
l hope you can find out the truth.

537
00:43:45,683 --> 00:43:47,082
What happened?

538
00:43:52,990 --> 00:43:55,424
That's what everyone keeps asking me.

539
00:43:55,793 --> 00:43:57,420
l want to find out the answer for myself.

540
00:45:45,068 --> 00:45:46,000
What's the matter?

541
00:45:46,436 --> 00:45:47,835
We're being followed.

542
00:46:36,353 --> 00:46:37,479
Why are you tailing me?

543
00:46:37,721 --> 00:46:38,779
l'm not.

544
00:46:39,389 --> 00:46:40,515
Are you a cop?

545
00:46:41,258 --> 00:46:43,021
- No.
- Janet, call the police.

546
00:46:43,293 --> 00:46:43,952
Miss, please don't!

547
00:46:52,569 --> 00:46:54,127
Hello? Police? l want to make a report.

548
00:46:56,440 --> 00:46:57,270
No!

549
00:47:07,951 --> 00:47:09,043
l'm here to help you.

550
00:47:12,222 --> 00:47:13,951
- Who are you?
- l'm from Singapore.

551
00:47:14,091 --> 00:47:15,058
Another secret agent?

552
00:47:15,259 --> 00:47:16,385
What? A Singaporean secret agent?

553
00:47:16,526 --> 00:47:17,584
What are you doing here?

554
00:47:19,196 --> 00:47:21,824
Something happened in Singapore.
The investigation brought me here.

555
00:47:23,000 --> 00:47:24,467
How much do you know
about your brother's murder?

556
00:47:29,940 --> 00:47:31,771
My name is Eric, Eric Ong.

557
00:47:32,242 --> 00:47:34,335
lf you get any information,
please call me.

558
00:47:34,511 --> 00:47:36,877
Why should he call you?
What good will it do him?

559
00:47:38,248 --> 00:47:39,579
We can pay you.

560
00:47:40,284 --> 00:47:41,308
How much?

561
00:47:44,354 --> 00:47:46,914
One hundred? One thousand?

562
00:47:47,557 --> 00:47:48,649
Or one million?

563
00:47:48,792 --> 00:47:50,726
We won't consider it
for less than 10 million.

564
00:47:52,396 --> 00:47:53,727
Do you think your information
is worth that much?

565
00:47:53,864 --> 00:47:56,196
Such an important case
is worth at least 10 million.

566
00:47:58,101 --> 00:47:59,329
l'll think about it.

567
00:48:03,106 --> 00:48:04,471
You'd better get going.

568
00:48:08,278 --> 00:48:09,472
What?

569
00:48:10,247 --> 00:48:11,612
Your film.

570
00:48:16,987 --> 00:48:18,682
- Thank you.
- You're welcome.

571
00:48:20,390 --> 00:48:21,982
Why'd you do that?

572
00:48:23,026 --> 00:48:24,584
He doesn't seem like a bad guy.

573
00:48:26,496 --> 00:48:27,121
Let's go.

574
00:48:29,299 --> 00:48:30,197
What do you want?

575
00:48:31,068 --> 00:48:32,000
This is my flat!

576
00:48:32,135 --> 00:48:33,534
Show me your l.D. please.

577
00:48:33,670 --> 00:48:34,898
And yours too.

578
00:48:35,372 --> 00:48:38,239
Are you kidding? You want to
check my l.D. in my own home?

579
00:48:40,043 --> 00:48:42,477
- Let them in.
- Yes sir!

580
00:48:42,746 --> 00:48:45,510
Are you for real?
You never asked to search my home!

581
00:48:45,649 --> 00:48:51,110
We just want to look for any new leads.

582
00:48:51,321 --> 00:48:52,413
Sorry for the inconvenience.

583
00:49:19,516 --> 00:49:20,915
Be careful, please.

584
00:49:38,869 --> 00:49:40,166
Why did you break my savings box?

585
00:49:40,904 --> 00:49:42,735
Aren't you going to apologize
and compensate him?

586
00:49:49,346 --> 00:49:50,608
What happened?

587
00:49:51,415 --> 00:49:55,545
l wanted to check what was under
the savings box, he shouted, and...

588
00:50:01,758 --> 00:50:03,089
Was this savings box yours?

589
00:50:04,728 --> 00:50:06,559
My brother and l
saved the money together.

590
00:50:10,600 --> 00:50:13,660
l am sorry.

591
00:50:16,673 --> 00:50:17,765
Officer Ng.

592
00:50:20,277 --> 00:50:21,301
Peter

593
00:50:25,949 --> 00:50:30,318
My brother's dead.
l just can't believe he's gone...

594
00:50:39,362 --> 00:50:42,126
Janet, my friend, Benny.

595
00:50:43,166 --> 00:50:44,599
My brother's girlfriend, Salina.

596
00:50:45,368 --> 00:50:47,359
- This is Thomas.
- Hi, how are you?

597
00:50:47,504 --> 00:50:49,335
l went with Thomas to pick you up
at the police station.

598
00:50:49,473 --> 00:50:51,100
But they said you'd already gone home.

599
00:50:52,309 --> 00:50:53,640
What are they doing here?

600
00:50:54,111 --> 00:50:55,703
They want to search the place again.

601
00:50:56,680 --> 00:50:57,738
What are they looking for?

602
00:50:57,914 --> 00:51:01,213
l don't know.
l don't think even they know.

603
00:51:02,085 --> 00:51:06,044
Really! May l ask who is in charge here?

604
00:51:07,858 --> 00:51:10,383
What do you want? We've got a warrant.

605
00:51:10,727 --> 00:51:11,716
Are you a lawyer?

606
00:51:11,862 --> 00:51:13,830
No, l'm not a lawyer.

607
00:51:13,964 --> 00:51:16,489
l am a judge. Salina is my friend,

608
00:51:16,666 --> 00:51:18,691
l came to help her
find out more about this case.

609
00:51:18,869 --> 00:51:19,927
Thomas Tsang

610
00:51:20,670 --> 00:51:22,399
Ronald Ng, G.S.U.

611
00:51:22,572 --> 00:51:25,132
l see, judging from your vast experience,

612
00:51:25,275 --> 00:51:27,436
You wouldn't allow an unnecessary search
or unlawful detention, right?

613
00:51:27,577 --> 00:51:30,842
And you wouldn't damage anything
not relevant to this case, right?

614
00:51:32,649 --> 00:51:33,809
l'll try my best.

615
00:52:02,679 --> 00:52:04,169
This computer is broken.

616
00:52:18,495 --> 00:52:19,519
Thank you.

617
00:52:28,338 --> 00:52:30,169
Be careful! Let me help you.

618
00:52:36,379 --> 00:52:38,870
What's this? A key!

619
00:52:39,082 --> 00:52:41,983
lt's Greg's key,
the key to a safety deposit box.

620
00:52:42,185 --> 00:52:43,618
- Call the police.
- No!

621
00:52:44,120 --> 00:52:45,382
We don't know what's inside.

622
00:52:45,555 --> 00:52:47,580
lf there is something
that might incriminate Greg,

623
00:52:47,724 --> 00:52:48,850
then we can burn it..

624
00:52:49,326 --> 00:52:51,317
Yes, we can check what's inside.

625
00:52:51,528 --> 00:52:52,995
Maybe we can sell it.

626
00:52:53,129 --> 00:52:55,222
But we need Greg's l.D. to open his box.

627
00:52:55,432 --> 00:52:56,592
l have his l.D. card.

628
00:52:56,766 --> 00:52:57,926
How about his signature?

629
00:52:58,802 --> 00:52:59,894
Practice forging it.

630
00:53:01,037 --> 00:53:02,527
This is illegal! You shouldn't do it.

631
00:53:05,542 --> 00:53:06,907
Your l.D. card, please.

632
00:53:14,384 --> 00:53:16,978
l love you.

633
00:53:18,054 --> 00:53:19,453
Mr. Li, please sign here.

634
00:53:19,589 --> 00:53:20,613
l'll get the key.

635
00:53:40,777 --> 00:53:41,937
Mr. Li, this way please.

636
00:53:59,529 --> 00:54:01,588
- lt's locked.
- Let's try and open it later.

637
00:56:02,085 --> 00:56:02,881
Get down!

638
00:58:11,047 --> 00:58:13,914
Relax. Just pretend
we're playing a videogame.

639
00:58:14,884 --> 00:58:17,819
But, if we lose, we can't put in
some coins for another round. Be careful!

640
00:58:18,254 --> 00:58:20,518
Where is Salina? Have you seen her?

641
00:58:21,558 --> 00:58:22,957
You'd better take care.

642
00:58:23,927 --> 00:58:25,417
Salina is a mystery.

643
00:58:25,895 --> 00:58:28,989
l couldn't find out
anything about her past.

644
00:58:44,881 --> 00:58:48,510
Don't worry, l've called for back-up.

645
00:58:49,419 --> 00:58:50,613
They're on the way.

646
00:58:52,121 --> 00:58:53,418
We just wait.

647
00:58:56,459 --> 00:58:57,949
This is business as usual
for a civil servant.

648
00:59:06,369 --> 00:59:07,427
Officer Ng!

649
00:59:09,439 --> 00:59:10,770
Officer Ng!

650
00:59:15,878 --> 00:59:18,369
Officer Ng!

651
00:59:19,716 --> 00:59:22,344
Wake up! Wake up!

652
00:59:49,412 --> 00:59:50,310
Get in!

653
00:59:54,350 --> 00:59:55,146
Move!

654
01:01:07,590 --> 01:01:09,217
What's inside?

655
01:01:10,059 --> 01:01:11,959
The key to a deposit box
at the Singapore National Bank.

656
01:01:12,829 --> 01:01:13,818
Which one?

657
01:01:14,597 --> 01:01:15,791
Where is it?

658
01:01:16,766 --> 01:01:17,960
lt's in Singapore.

659
01:01:28,878 --> 01:01:31,039
Janet, listen.

660
01:01:31,180 --> 01:01:33,580
Salina and l need to fly to Singapore.

661
01:01:33,783 --> 01:01:36,718
Bring my passport
and meet me at the airport.

662
01:01:36,919 --> 01:01:39,080
And bring me some clothes.

663
01:01:39,889 --> 01:01:42,824
There's no time to explain. Just hurry!

664
01:01:52,935 --> 01:01:56,098
They won't kill you for a birth
certificate or a graduation document.

665
01:01:56,339 --> 01:01:57,738
What was Greg involved in?

666
01:01:57,907 --> 01:01:59,033
What did he leave in Singapore?

667
01:01:59,375 --> 01:02:00,706
Janet and l are coming with you.

668
01:02:01,077 --> 01:02:02,544
We're not going there to play around!

669
01:02:02,678 --> 01:02:04,737
l know, l just want to back you up.

670
01:02:05,381 --> 01:02:07,076
You, okay, but what about Janet?

671
01:02:07,250 --> 01:02:08,842
lf you can convince her, go ahead.

672
01:02:10,219 --> 01:02:11,311
Have you bought the tickets?

673
01:02:13,089 --> 01:02:13,987
What's up?

674
01:02:14,223 --> 01:02:16,384
lt's too dangerous. You'd better not go.

675
01:02:16,893 --> 01:02:17,757
What about you?

676
01:02:17,894 --> 01:02:19,361
l can handle it myself.

677
01:02:19,729 --> 01:02:21,629
This cheque is for you.

678
01:02:23,432 --> 01:02:24,558
Why are you giving me so much money?

679
01:02:24,700 --> 01:02:26,065
l know you need it.

680
01:02:26,269 --> 01:02:28,066
lf l find anything valuable,

681
01:02:28,204 --> 01:02:29,933
l'll bring it back to you.

682
01:02:30,373 --> 01:02:31,806
Why are you taking this risk?

683
01:02:32,608 --> 01:02:34,098
He was my fiance.

684
01:02:34,277 --> 01:02:35,767
He was my brother.

685
01:02:36,179 --> 01:02:37,976
My only brother.

686
01:02:38,781 --> 01:02:40,510
l must find out the truth.

687
01:02:44,620 --> 01:02:46,520
One whole GSU unit was wiped out.

688
01:02:46,656 --> 01:02:47,816
Who did it?

689
01:02:48,024 --> 01:02:49,719
They were ambushed by Kelvin's men.

690
01:02:50,059 --> 01:02:52,152
l think they wanted something from Peter.

691
01:02:52,795 --> 01:02:55,025
- ls it the program?
- l'm not sure.

692
01:02:55,331 --> 01:02:56,559
l don't think Peter knows either.

693
01:02:56,699 --> 01:02:58,166
Are you sure this guy's not involved?

694
01:02:58,301 --> 01:02:59,632
Peter is clean, sir.

695
01:03:00,336 --> 01:03:01,564
So where is he now?

696
01:03:02,104 --> 01:03:03,366
He got away.

697
01:03:03,739 --> 01:03:06,902
A whole G.S.U. team wiped out,
and he escaped? How?

698
01:03:08,077 --> 01:03:09,704
Well, that girl Salina.

699
01:03:09,912 --> 01:03:11,345
She... she drove him.

700
01:03:12,048 --> 01:03:13,538
And you... what did you do?

701
01:03:15,852 --> 01:03:17,979
l...

702
01:03:21,057 --> 01:03:24,390
- l fired a few shots, sir...
- You fired a few shots?

703
01:03:25,261 --> 01:03:26,421
l had no choice, sir!

704
01:03:26,562 --> 01:03:28,291
You are right, that is not a choice.

705
01:03:28,431 --> 01:03:31,059
l can't have a Singapore agent
starting a war with the ClA.

706
01:03:31,200 --> 01:03:33,964
Sir, sir, just a tiny one.

707
01:03:34,103 --> 01:03:35,092
Look, l don't care, all right.

708
01:03:35,238 --> 01:03:37,570
You were supposed
to keep this thing low profile,

709
01:03:37,707 --> 01:03:39,072
And now you are making
headlines over there!

710
01:03:39,242 --> 01:03:40,436
You better come back to Singapore now.

711
01:03:40,877 --> 01:03:42,970
- Sir...
- And one more thing,

712
01:03:43,145 --> 01:03:45,010
Where did you get the weapon?

713
01:03:45,882 --> 01:03:47,941
l don't think you want to know sir...

714
01:04:28,224 --> 01:04:29,486
Does it fit?

715
01:04:30,826 --> 01:04:31,952
Yes, thank you.

716
01:04:45,942 --> 01:04:48,410
Are you going to forge
your brother's name again tomorrow?

717
01:04:48,978 --> 01:04:51,037
Why won't you listen to me?
Call the police!

718
01:04:51,681 --> 01:04:52,841
Call Eric.

719
01:04:52,982 --> 01:04:55,382
Didn't you say he saved
your life at the car park?

720
01:04:58,054 --> 01:04:58,884
What do you think?

721
01:04:59,021 --> 01:05:01,353
lt's up to you. Do what you want.

722
01:05:01,524 --> 01:05:03,355
l just don't want
to share a room with Janet.

723
01:05:03,492 --> 01:05:05,289
There's only one bed, l'm not used to it.

724
01:05:05,628 --> 01:05:07,425
There are two beds in Benny's room.

725
01:05:09,332 --> 01:05:10,458
That's fine by me!

726
01:05:26,082 --> 01:05:27,481
What's your problem?

727
01:05:30,753 --> 01:05:32,243
Ever since the ambush in the car park,

728
01:05:32,688 --> 01:05:35,156
You've looked at me
like l'm your enemy. Why?

729
01:05:37,059 --> 01:05:38,754
l really want to know something.

730
01:05:39,662 --> 01:05:41,323
Why weren't you hurt in the car park?

731
01:05:42,565 --> 01:05:44,965
How did you drive my car without my key?

732
01:05:46,135 --> 01:05:47,500
How come you carry
a set of skeleton keys?

733
01:05:47,903 --> 01:05:50,633
Officer Ng told me that you have no past.

734
01:05:50,773 --> 01:05:52,035
Just who the hell are you?

735
01:05:52,541 --> 01:05:53,803
How did you meet my brother?

736
01:06:04,887 --> 01:06:06,286
l wasn't called Salina then.

737
01:06:07,690 --> 01:06:08,987
When l first knew your brother,

738
01:06:09,125 --> 01:06:11,116
l was a club girl
in a Singapore nightclub.

739
01:06:16,399 --> 01:06:19,266
l was a hooker before, okay?

740
01:06:20,069 --> 01:06:22,629
l know how to steal cars.

741
01:06:26,175 --> 01:06:27,733
l met your brother at the nightclub.

742
01:06:28,377 --> 01:06:30,641
He asked me to go to the USA with him.

743
01:06:33,783 --> 01:06:35,273
So l became his secretary.

744
01:06:44,326 --> 01:06:46,055
He wanted me to forget my past.

745
01:06:48,064 --> 01:06:51,261
Salina is the name he liked most.

746
01:07:11,120 --> 01:07:13,247
Let's call the police tomorrow morning.

747
01:07:15,925 --> 01:07:17,517
Let's convince Peter together.

748
01:07:18,160 --> 01:07:18,785
All right.

749
01:07:20,570 --> 01:07:22,037
What's wrong with the memory?

750
01:07:22,739 --> 01:07:23,831
Trying to mess with me?

751
01:07:25,108 --> 01:07:26,803
l'll show you who's boss!

752
01:07:29,279 --> 01:07:31,008
Okay, l'll fix you tomorrow.

753
01:07:33,884 --> 01:07:35,044
l'm going to bed now.

754
01:07:39,956 --> 01:07:43,323
This is the first time
l've experienced such feelings...

755
01:07:44,461 --> 01:07:45,689
What feelings?

756
01:07:46,596 --> 01:07:49,429
l think l'm in love.

757
01:08:00,343 --> 01:08:01,241
Goodnight!

758
01:08:02,579 --> 01:08:03,637
Goodnight.

759
01:08:23,266 --> 01:08:24,062
Where is Salina?

760
01:08:24,201 --> 01:08:25,828
She's changing.

761
01:08:26,036 --> 01:08:28,402
You know, women take
a long time to get changed.

762
01:08:28,538 --> 01:08:30,369
l've been waiting for an hour.

763
01:08:35,746 --> 01:08:40,206
Salina...

764
01:08:44,254 --> 01:08:45,551
Salina...

765
01:08:59,269 --> 01:09:01,533
Miss, where are the safety deposit boxes?

766
01:09:02,172 --> 01:09:04,140
Over there, sir, down the stairs.

767
01:09:46,783 --> 01:09:48,216
You got to help us! Help us!

768
01:09:48,418 --> 01:09:52,047
Go... get the red car. Go... go...

769
01:09:58,528 --> 01:10:01,190
There is a car jack on Battery Road,
all units respond.

770
01:10:01,331 --> 01:10:03,856
Car jacking proceeding on Battery Road,

771
01:10:04,000 --> 01:10:05,592
heading for North Bridge Road
is driving a police car.

772
01:14:11,414 --> 01:14:12,312
Want some candy?

773
01:14:14,184 --> 01:14:15,242
Okay.

774
01:14:21,491 --> 01:14:22,788
l want to talk to you.

775
01:14:33,503 --> 01:14:34,401
Do you want to arrest us?

776
01:14:37,407 --> 01:14:39,773
My orders are to get you back
to Hong Kong as soon as possible.

777
01:14:41,811 --> 01:14:43,176
The HK police need you
to help with their investigation

778
01:14:43,313 --> 01:14:44,712
of the gun battle in the car park.

779
01:14:46,850 --> 01:14:47,942
l want your help.

780
01:14:49,919 --> 01:14:51,511
Don't tell them l was there.

781
01:14:52,555 --> 01:14:54,887
Otherwise, l'll be in deep shit.

782
01:14:56,626 --> 01:14:57,684
Thank you for saving me.

783
01:14:59,195 --> 01:15:00,560
Sorry l couldn't save your brother.

784
01:15:02,165 --> 01:15:03,530
Do you know who wanted him dead?

785
01:15:06,236 --> 01:15:08,466
Knowing too much isn't good for you.

786
01:15:09,939 --> 01:15:11,497
But l can tell you one thing.

787
01:15:11,841 --> 01:15:13,968
l believe your brother was innocent.

788
01:15:18,548 --> 01:15:19,572
How about Salina?

789
01:15:23,086 --> 01:15:24,678
l've already said too much.

790
01:15:25,221 --> 01:15:26,711
Just forget it.

791
01:15:27,190 --> 01:15:28,248
